org.hibernate.query.sqm.consume.multitable.spi.idtable.AbstractTableBasedStrategy

  • Packages that use AbstractTableBasedStrategy 
    Package Description
    org.hibernate.query.sqm.consume.multitable.spi.idtable
    Support for IdTableStrategy implementations which are backed by an "id table" which is used to temporarily store the ids of entities matching the update/delete restrictions.

    • Uses of AbstractTableBasedStrategy in org.hibernate.query.sqm.consume.multitable.spi.idtable

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  GlobalTemporaryTableStrategy
      Strategy based on ANSI SQL's definition of a "global temporary table".
      class  LocalTemporaryTableStrategy
      Strategy based on ANSI SQL's definition of a "local temporary table" (local to each db session).
      class  PersistentTableStrategy
      This is a strategy that mimics temporary tables for databases which do not support temporary tables.
